task.summary: Improved listing of backups. Fixed a bug that occured when backup and original had different roots.
Implemented word wrapping for the backup listing.
A few tweaks here and there for a more fool proof design. Added some error messages.
Added a command line argument to delete backups + a few tweaks in the command line viewer and ProgramPaths.
